1. We need to create a class name

  Example: class Siva
  
  
2. We neeed to create a Main method
 
   public static void main(String[]args)
   {
   
   }
   
3. We need to define the body of the main method

   public static void main(String[]args)
   {
      System.out.println("Hello siva");
   }



class Siva
{
    public static void main(Strin[]args)
    {
        
      System.out.println("Sivathanu");
    
    }

}


4. Save the file in .java formate.
5. It will create the class file
6. Run the class file.


Note:
